OL,3,CComments under PSNI job advert deemed
OL,4,Cracist by police body
OL,6,FThe Policing Board has condemned
OL,7,F"negative and racist" online
OL,8,Fcommentary following the launch of a
OL,9,Fnew PSNI recruitment drive.
OL,11,FThe police service launched its first
OL,12,Fstudent officer recruitment programme
OL,13,Fsince 2021 earlier this week, aiming
OL,14,Fto lift officer numbers from an all-
OL,15,Ftime low of 6,300.
OL,17,FOne of the recruitment advertisements
OL,18,Ffeatures an image of a female officer
OL,19,Ffrom an ethnic minority background.
