OL,6,FPosts which appeared on social media
OL,7,Fabout the ad were condemned at a
OL,8,Fmeeting of the board's Resources
OL,9,FCommittee on Thursday.
OL,11,FCommittee chairman Trevor Clarke MLA
OL,12,Fsaid: "Policing must be reflective and
OL,13,Frepresentative of the community it
OL,14,Fserves, and the board fully supports
OL,15,Fthe PSNI campaign and outreach work
OL,16,Fbeing undertaken to encourage
OL,17,Fapplications so that the service is
OL,18,Ffully representative of the diversity
OL,19,Fof our community.
