OL,6,F"A strong message must be sent that
OL,7,Fracism in any form is not acceptable
OL,8,Fand must be called out."
OL,10,FThe PSNI's chief operating officer,
OL,11,FPamela McCreedy, said they will
OL,12,Fcontinue to reach out to encourage
OL,13,Fpeople from all communities to apply
OL,14,Ffor a career in policing.
OL,16,F"The Police Service of Northern
OL,17,FIreland is committed to being
OL,18,Frepresentative of the communities we
OL,19,Fserve," she said.
